Package: fsmr
Type: Package
Title: Trip-Based Four-Step Transport Demand Modeling in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Nelson de Oliveira", "Quesado Filho", email = "nquesado@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Francisco Moraes", "de Oliveira Neto", email = "moraes@det.ufc.br", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Provides data structures and modeling tools for preparing
    zone-level, origin-destination survey, and origin-destination demand
    data. Implements production and attraction summaries, regression and
    classification-rate generation models, growth-factor projections, custom
    generation methods, matrix visualization, and matrix re-aggregation as
    foundations for trip-based four-step transport demand modeling. Trips are
    represented as independent choice units; trip-chaining and activity-based
    models are outside the current scope.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
